Say hello to <b>Sandra</b>, our Featured Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Sandra has been living in Millsberry since July 24th, 2007. She loves relaxing at her charming, <a href="http://millsberry.com/home/?user=pr_gurl15"><a href='/home/?user=pr_gurl15'>68896-C Main Street</a> home, in Metro Park</a>. <br><br>The Metro Park neighborhood has been a perfect fit for Sandra. So close to downtown, it truly puts all of Millsberry's offerings at her fingertips! <br><br>Sandra has been quite busy since she moved to Millsberry. She's managed to rack up a whopping 16 trophies, for games ranging from Sudoku to Intergalactic Defender. <br><br>Sandra describes herself as very athletic&mdash;and with trophies from Tricky Touchdown, Sink Three, and Home Run Derby, we'll take her word for it. <br><br>She also happens to be very creative. Her favorite colors are green, black, and gray. You may just see them in her next painting! <br><br>If you're planning on jamming out with Sandra, you'll enjoy a wide variety of tunes. She's into pop, classical, and modern rock. Talk about music to your ears!<br><br>Next time you see Sandra, be sure to congratulate her and thank her for being such an outstanding citizen!<br></div>
